ferent%20aspects%20of%20the%20crypto%20value%20chain%20that%20are%20happening%20in%20traditionally%20red%20states%20or%20traditionally%20blue%20states%2C%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standwithcrypto.org%2Fpoliticians%3FswcStanceScore%3DPro-crypto%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20pro-crypto%20politician%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20DC%20is%20Cynthia%20Lummis%2C%20a%20first-term%20Republican%20senator%20from%20Wyoming.%20She%20was%20reportedly%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2020%2F11%2F04%2Fwyoming-bitcoin-cynthia-lummis-u-s-senate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20Senator%20to%20own%20bitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lummis.senate.gov%2Fpress-releases%2Flummis-wyden-raise-alarm-biden-doj-is-criminalizing-core-tenants-of-bitcoin-network-decentralized-finance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiercely%20critical%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Biden%20administration%20regulations%20that%20she%20saw%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverywhere%20you%20looked%20in%20the%20regulatory%20framework%2C%20it%20was%20hostile%2C%26quot%3B%20Lummis%20said%20on%20stage%20at%20the%20Bitcoin%20Investor%20Week%20conference.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20hostility%20was%20pointed%20at%20not%20just%20bitcoin%2C%20but%20other%20digital%20assets%3A%20ethereum%2C%20cardano%2C%20solana%20%E2%80%94%20all%20this%20stuff.%20But%20bitcoin%20was%20caught%20up%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Democratic%20Party%20representative%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELummis%20thinks%20attitudes%20toward%20crypto%20are%20now%20shifting%2C%20and%20she's%20looking%20to%20have%20conversations%20with%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%20about%20how%20the%20US%20should%20approach%20this%20growing%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbd2637b-7054-4f26-b428-d79662d75731%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Dems%20get%20their%20arms%20around%20crypto%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20believe%20Democrats%20are%20warming%20up%20to%20crypto%2C%20others%20aren't%20holding%20their%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Scaramucci%2C%20a%20major%20crypto%20investor%20and%20an%20avowed%20Trump%20critic%2C%20said%20at%20the%20bitcoin%20conference%20that%20he%20agreed%20with%20Lummis's%20assessment%20about%20Democrats.%20Under%20Biden%2C%20he%20said%20the%20party%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20out%20to%20lunch%26quot%3B%20last%20year%20when%20it%20came%20to%20crypto%20and%20blockchain%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMark%20Cuban%2C%20Michael%20Novogratz%2C%20and%20I%20last%20summer%20descended%20into%20the%20White%20House%2C%20descended%20into%20meetings%20in%20Washington%20with%20senators%2C%20policymakers%2C%20assistant%20secretaries%20to%20the%20Treasury%2C%26quot%3B%20Scaramucci%20said%20at%20the%20conference.%20He%20said%20the%20tech%20leaders%20told%20Biden's%20team%3A%20%26quot%3B'What%20are%20you%20guys%20doing%3F%20You've%20got%20to%20get%20off%20the%20anti-crypto%20brigade.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20outdated%20stance%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20thing%20that%20Trump%20has%20going%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Scaramucci%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20the%20Democrats%20didn't%20see%20that%20and%20didn't%20see%20the%20power%20of%20this%20industry%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20they%20are%20derelict%20in%20their%20duties%20right%20now%20and%20aren't%20really%20understanding%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20marketplace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SkyBridge%20Capital%20founder%20is%20trying%20to%20turn%20the%20tide%2C%20so%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20begrudgingly%20give%20Trump%20props.%20He%20told%20BI%20last%20fall%20that%20the%2045th%20president's%20win%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-risk-outlook-trump-deportation-tariff-