ancial-mar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Tariff%20Announcement%20That%20Shocked%20Financial%20Markets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20question%20is%20do%20we%20then%20see%20jobs%20being%20lost%2C%20Particularly%20because%20these%20taxes%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20focused%20on%20complicated%20supply%20chains%20than%20was%20the%20case%20back%20in%202018%2C%20that%20may%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20disruptive%20to%20the%20economy%20and%20potentially%20could%20create%20unemployment%20or%20just%20fear%20of%20unemployment%2C%20which%20would%20lower%20demand%2C%20and%20that%20would%20then%20be%20a%20disinflation%20force%2C%20but%20not%20now%20%E2%80%94%20a%20disinflation%20force%20in%20the%20future%20accompanied%20by%20significantly%20lower%20growth.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246bc5bfa-904f-466f-9b65-f9aac6e2f9f7%5C%22%3EMatthew%20C.%20Klein%2C%20The%20Overshoot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheovershoot.co%2Fp%2Fthe-us-chooses-stagflation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20US%20Chooses%20Stagflation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWhile%20every%20jurisdiction%20has%20room%20for%20improvement%2C%20the%20US%20business%20environment%20has%20materially%20worsened%20in%20the%20past%20six%20weeks.%20Perhaps%20most%20striking%20is%20not%20just%20the%20actual%20changes%20that%20have%20been%20announced%2C%20but%20the%20volatility%20and%20uncertainty%20around%20those%20changes.%20Discriminatory%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20are%20almost%20uniquely%20pointless%20acts%20of%20self-harm%2C%20for%20example%2C%20but%20discriminatory%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20that%20keep%20changing%20are%20worse.%20People%20can%20adapt%20to%20bad%20policies%2C%20but%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20adapt%20when%20both%20the%20end%20state%20and%20even%20the%20direction%20of%20tra