3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20needs%20to%20question%20its%20training%20data%20and%20take%20counterintuitive%20approaches%2C%20the%20Hugging%20Face%20exec%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWolf's%20comments%20come%20as%20tech%20focuses%20on%20agentic%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20excels%20at%20following%20instructions%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20not%20pushing%20the%20boundaries%20of%20knowledge%2C%20said%20Thomas%20Wolf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20science%20officer%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Hugging%20Face%2C%20an%20open-source%20AI%20company%20backed%20by%20Amazon%20and%20Nvidia%2C%20analyzed%20the%20limits%20of%20large%20language%20models%20in%20a%20Thursday%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20that%20the%20field%20produces%20%26quot%3Boverly%20compliant%20helpers%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20revolutionaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20AI%20isn't%20creating%20new%20knowledge%2C%20Wolf%20wrote.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20just%20filling%20in%20the%20blanks%20between%20existing%20facts%20%E2%80%94%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bmanifold%20filling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolf%20argues%20that%20for%20AI%20to%20drive%20real%20scientific%20breakthroughs%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20do%20more%20than%20retrieve%20and%20synthesize%20information.%20AI%20should%20question%20its%20own%20training%20data%2C%20take%20counterintuitive%20approaches%2C%20generate%20new%20ideas%20from%20minimal%20input%2C%20and%20ask%20unexpected%20questions%20that%20open%20new%20research%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolf%20also%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bcompressed%2021st%20century%26quot%3B%E2%80%94%20a%20concept%20from%20an%20October%20essay%20by%20Anthropic's%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%2C%20%26quot%3BMachine%20of%20Loving%20Grace.%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20wrote%20that%20AI%20could%20accelerate%20scientific%20progress%20so%20much%20that%20discoveries%20expected%20over%20the%20next%20100%20years%20could%20happen%20in%20just%20five%20to%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20r