20of%20India%20(CJI)%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20leading%20a%20bench%20that%20included%20Justice%20PV%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20remarked%20orally%20that%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court's%20decision%20was%20justified%20as%20the%20railway%20line%20would%20also%20be%20developed%20and%20incorporated%20into%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20and%20Adani%20Properties%20and%20has%20scheduled%20the%20next%20hearing%20for%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeclink%20Technologies%2C%20which%20had%20originally%20bid%20Rs%207%2C200%20crore%20for%20the%20Dharavi%20redevelopment%2C%20informed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20was%20willing%20to%20increase%20its%20offer%20by%2020%20per%20cent.%20The%20bench%20directed%20Seclink%20to%20submit%20an%20affidavit%20detailing%20its%20revised%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202024%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20Maharashtra%20government's%20decision%20to%20cancel%20Seclink's%202019%20bid%20and%20issue%20a%20fresh%20tender%20in%202022%2C%20ultimately%20awarding%20the%20project%20to%20Adani%20Group.%20Seclink%20subsequently%20appealed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20justified%20its%20decision%2C%20citing%20changes%20in%20economic%20conditions%20between%202019%20and%202022%2C%20including%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20currency%20fluctuations%2C%20and%20rising%20interest%20rates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741333140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F0f2qfsl8_dharavi_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-halt-dharavi-redevelopment-project-7868489%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%