2%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-retaliate-trump-trade-war-tariffs-soybeans-agriculture-two-sessions-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eretaliatory%2025%25%20tariffs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%24155%20billion%20worth%20of%20American%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Gregory%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Kentucky%20Distillers'%20Association%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20statement%20on%20X%20that%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20would%20have%20%26quot%3Bfar-reaching%20consequences%20across%20Kentucky%2C%20home%20to%2095%25%20of%20the%20world's%20bourbon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanada's%20retaliatory%20measures%20will%20%26quot%3Bjeopardize%20growth%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGregory's%20statement%20comes%20as%20several%20Canadian%20provinces%20have%20clamped%20down%20on%20US-made%20alcohol%20this%20week.%20Provinces%20like%20Ontario%20and%20New%20Brunswick%20instructed%20state-affiliated%20alcohol%20retailers%2C%20which%20regulate%20the%20sale%20and%20distribution%20of%20alcohol%20in%20their%20regions%2C%20to%20pull%20US%20products%20from%20their%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOntario's%20government%20instructed%20the%20Liquor%20Control%20Board%20of%20Ontario%20to%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%26quot%3B%20cease%20imports%20of%20US%20alcohol%20and%20stop%20selling%20American%20products%2C%20the%20LCBO%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20government%20of%20New%20Brunswick%20said%20on%20Facebook%20that%20it%20would%20not%20purchase%20any%20new%20US%20alcohol%20products.%20The%20government%20said%20it%20had%20removed%20US-made%20alcohol%20products%20from%20the%20shelves%20of%20Alcool%20NB%2C%20a%20government-affiliated%20alcohol%20retailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuebec%20followed%20suit.%20The%20Soci%C3%A9t%C3%A9%20des%20alcools%20du%20Qu%C3%A9bec%2C%20a%20government-run%20alcohol%20retailer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20X%20post%20that%20it%20was%20wiping%20all%20US%20products%20from%20branches%20and%20its%20website%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20request%20of%20the%20Qu%C3%A9bec%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20trade%20war%20kicked%20off%2C%20Canada%20was%20a%20large%20importer%20of%20Kentucky-made%20spirits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Canada-Kentucky%20agricultural%20trade%20totaled%20%24691%20million%20in%202023%2C%20with%20Kentucky%20exporting%20%2443%20million%20worth%20of%20whiskey%20to%20Canada%20that%20year%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20said%20on%20its%20official%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKentucky%20imported%20%2440.3%20million%20worth%20of%20whiskey%20from%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Coomes%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Louisville%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%202023%20report%20that%20Canada%20was%20the%20biggest%20importer%20of%20Kentucky-made%20spirits%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Kentucky%20bourbon%20makers%20who%20lamented%20Canada's%20retaliatory%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawson%20Whiting%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Brown-Forman%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Jack%20Daniel's%2C%20said%20on%20a%20Wednesday%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-daniels-exec-canada-barring-their-liquor-disproportionate-response-tariffs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretaliation%20was%20%26quot%3Bworse%20than%20a%20tariff%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%20response%26quot%3B%20to%20Trump's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20its%20annual%20report%20that%20Canada%20accounted%20for%201%25%20of%20total%20sales%2C%20while%2045%25%20came%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20in%20early%20February%20that%20he%20would%20impose%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mexico-canada-china-tariffs-january-20-trade-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E25%2