le%20the%20chances%20are%20rather%20low%2C%20one%20cannot%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20tied%20match.%20After%20all%2C%20New%20Zealand%20agonisingly%20suffered%20defeat%20in%20the%202019%20World%20Cup%20final%20despite%20tying%20the%20game.%20But%20who%20wins%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20if%20the%20final%20ends%20in%20a%20tie%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20if%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20final%20ends%20in%20a%20tie%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20final%20ending%20in%20a%20tie%2C%20a%20Super%20Over%20will%20take%20place%20to%20decide%20the%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20tie%20in%20the%20Super%20Over%2C%20multiple%20Super%20Overs%20will%20be%20played%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20final%20until%20we%20get%20a%20clear%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20to%20prevent%20a%20situation%20like%20the%202019%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20where%20New%20Zealand%20lost%20to%20England%20on%20boundary%20count%20despite%20tying%20both%20the%20regulation%2050-over%20match%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Super%20Over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20if%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20final%20is%20washed%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERain%20has%20played%20spoilsport%20in%20as%20many%20as%20three%20games%20in%20Pakistan%20during%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%20but%20largely%20stayed%20away%20in%20Dubai%2C%20where%20India's%20games%20have%20taken%20place.%20Rain%20is%20still%20very%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20for%20the%20final%2C%20which%20will%20also%20be%20held%20at%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20off%20chance%20of%20a%20rain%20washout%2C%20both%20teams%20will%20share%20the%20trophy.%20This%20has%20already%20happened%20once%20previously%20in%20a%20Champions%20Trophy%20final.%20In%202002%2C%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20shared%20the%20trophy%20after%20the%20game%20couldn't%20be%20completed%20due%20to%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Champions%20Trophy%202002%20final%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20controversial%20ICC%20finals%2C%20where%20more%20than%20110%20overs%20were%20played%20across%20two%20days%2C%20but%20the%20game%20couldn't%20be%20completed%20due%20to%20it%20being%20restarted%20from%20scratch%20on%20the%20second%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20vs%20New%20Zealand%3A%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20final%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20enter%20the%20final%20as%20firm%20favourites%2C%20having%20won%20seven%20ODI%20matches%20on%20the%20trot%2C%20including%20beating%20New%20Zealand%20in%20their%20Group%20A%20game.%20With%20the%20game%20taking%20place%20in%20Dubai%2C%20India%20will%20also%20enjoy%20the%20familiarity%20of%20playing%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20New%20Zealand%20put%20up%20a%20dominant%20display%20with%20the%20bat%20in%20the%20semi-final%20against%20South%20Africa.%20The%20key%20for%20them%20would%20be%20to%20handle%20the%20Indian%20spinners%20better.%20Mystery%20spinner%20Varun%20Chakravarthy%20had%20taken%20a%20fifer%20in%20the%20previous%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741330560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fi5annob_india-vs-new-zealand_625x300_07_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhat-happens-if-the-india-vs-new-zealand-champions-trophy-2025-final-ends-in-a-tie-scenarios-explained-7867756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20final%20ended%20in%20a%20tied%20match%20or%20was%20washed%20out%20due%20to%20rain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhat-happens-if-the-india-vs-new-zealand-champions-trophy-2025-final-ends-in-a-tie-scenarios-explained-7867756%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A