C%2Fa%3E%20on%20non-Hindi%20speakers%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20urged%20the%20state%20government%20to%20introduce%20medical%20and%20engineering%20courses%20in%20Tamil.%20Mr%20Shah%20claimed%20that%20the%20DMK%20chief%20has%20not%20done%20enough%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20that%20it%20is%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20that%20has%20made%20key%20changes%20to%20recruitment%20policies%20to%20accommodate%20regional%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20now%2C%20there%20was%20no%20place%20for%20the%20mother%20tongue%20in%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%20Constable%20recruitment.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20decided%20that%20our%20youth%20will%20now%20be%20able%20to%20write%20their%20CAPF%20exam%20in%20all%20languages%20in%20the%20Eighth%20Schedule%2C%20including%20Tamil%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Shah.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20urge%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20take%20steps%20towards%20introducing%20the%20curriculum%20of%20medical%20and%20engineering%20courses%20in%20Tamil%20language%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20approved%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20CAPF%20examination%20in%2013%20regional%20languages%2C%20including%20Tamil%2C%20in%202023%2C%20days%20after%20Mr%20Stalin%20had%20protested%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20CAPF%20to%20conduct%20it%20only%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20long%20social%20media%20post%20today%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20attempting%20to%20impose%20Hindi%20through%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP).%20He%20cited%20the%20BJP's%20efforts%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20linguistic%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tree%20may%20prefer%20calm%2C%20but%20the%20wind%20will%20not%20subside%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20controversy%20was%20provoked%20by%20the%20Union%20Education%20Minister's%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20who%20provoked%20us%20to%20write%20this%20series%20of%20letters%20when%20we%20were%20simply%20doing%20our%20job.%20He%20forgot%20his%20place%20and%20dared%20to%20threaten%20an%20entire%20state%20to%20accept%20Hindi%20Imposition%2C%20and%20now%20he%20faces%20the%20consequences%20of%20reviving%20a%20fight%20he%20can%20never%20win.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20not%20be%20blackmailed%20into%20surrendering%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20had%20already%20achieved%20what%20the%20NEP%20aimed%20for%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20an%20LKG%20student%20lecturing%20a%20PhD%20holder.%20Dravidam%20does%20not%20take%20dictations%20from%20Delhi.%20Instead%2C%20it%20sets%20the%20course%20for%20the%20nation%20to%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20took%20aim%20at%20the%20BJP's%20recent%20signature%20campaign%20supporting%20the%20NEP%20and%20the%20three-language%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20the%20BJP's%20circus-like%20signature%20campaign%20for%20the%20three-language%20formula%20has%20become%20a%20laughing%20stock%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20I%20challenge%20them%20to%20make%20this%20their%20core%20agenda%20in%20the%202026%20Assembly%20elections%20and%20let%20it%20be%20a%20referendum%20on%20Hindi%20imposition%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%202020%2C%20recommends%20a%20three-language%20formula%2C%20though%20it%20explicitly%20states%20that%20no%20language%20will%20be%20imposed%20on%20any%20state.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20policy%20has%20found%20no%20traction%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20insists%20that%20the%20existing%20two-language%20system%20is%20sufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20argues%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20flourished%20under%20the%20current%20system%20and%20sees%20no%20need%20for%20an%20additional%20language.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20BJP%20maintains%20that%20the%20three-language%20formula%20would%20benefit%20people%20when%20they%20travel%20to%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20historical%20precedents%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20claimed%20that%20every%20attempt%20to%20impose%20Hindi%20on%20Tamil%20Nadu%20had%20been%20met%20with%20resistance%2C%20leading%20either%20to%20the%20defeat%20of%20the%20proponents%20or%20their%20eventual%20alignment%20with%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistory%20is%20clear.%20Those%20who%20tried%20to%20impose%20Hindi%20on%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20either%20been%20defeated%20or%20later%20changed%20their%20stance%20and%20aligned%20with%20DMK.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20not%20tolerate%20Hindi%20colonialism%20replacing%20British%20colonialism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20excessively%20using%20Hindi%20in%20the%20names%20of%20schemes%2C%20awards%2C%20and%20government%20institutions%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20suffocating%20non-Hindi%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20names%20of%20schemes%20to%20awards%20to%20Union%20government%20institutions%2C%20Hindi%20has%20been%20imposed%20to%20a%20nauseating%20extent%2C%20suffocating%20non-Hindi%20speakers%2C%20who%20are%20the%20majority%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%20%26quot%3BMen%20may%20come%2C%20men%20may%20go.%20But%20even%20long%20after%20the%20dominance%20of%20Hindi%20is%20shattered%20in%20India%2C%20history%20will%20remember%20that%20it%20was%20DMK%20that%20stood%20as%20the%20vanguard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20President%20K%20Annamalai%20hit%20back%20at%20Mr%20Stalin%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%20drama%26quot%3B%20over%20Hindi%20imposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThiru%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20our%20online%20signature%20campaign%20through%20PuthiyaKalvi.in%20is%20supported%20by%20over%202%20lak