tes%20%26quot%3BHigh%20Tariff%26quot%3B%20Remark%20On%20India%20In%20%26quot%3BBig%20One%20On...%26quot%3B%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20very%20high%20tariff%20nation%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20said%20as%20he%20reiterated%20that%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20that%20impose%20levies%20on%20American%20goods%20will%20kick%20in%20on%20April%202.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20the%20big%20one%20will%20be%20on%20April%202%2C%20when%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20so%20if%20India%20or%20China%2C%20or%20any%20of%20the%20countries%20that%20really%E2%80%A6India%20is%20a%20very%20high%20tariff%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20tell%20you%20what's%20a%20high%20tariff%20nation%20-%20it's%20Canada.%20Canada%20charges%20us%20250%25%20for%20our%20milk%20product%20and%20other%20products%2C%20and%20a%20tremendous%20tariff%20with%20lumber%20and%20things%20as%20such.%20And%20yet%20we%20don't%20need%20their%20lumber.%20We%20have%20more%20lumber%20than%20they%20do.%20We%20don't%20need%20Canada's%20lumber%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trump%20said%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20on%20Thursday%20as%20he%20signed%20some%20executive%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20said%20right%20now%2C%20the%20tariffs%20are%20%E2%80%9Ctemporary%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20ones%E2%80%9D%20but%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20predominant%20tariffs%E2%80%9D%20that%20will%20be%20reciprocal%20in%20nature%2C%20will%20start%20from%20April%202%20and%20they%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20game%20changer%20for%20our%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20we've%20been%20ripped%20off%20by%20every%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20now%20whatever%20they%20charge%20us%2C%20they%20charge%20us%20150-200%25%20(and)%20we%20charge%20them%20nothing.%20So%20whatever%20they%20charge%20us%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20charge%20them%2C%20and%20there'll%20be%20no%20getting%20out%20of%20it.%20So%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20April%202.%20I've%20been%20looking%20forward%20to%20that%20date%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20And%20that'll%20be%20something%20very%20big%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20as%20many%20days%20that%20Trump%20has%20remarked%20about%20India's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20to%20the%20joint%20session%20of%20Congress%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20first%20of%20his%20second%20term%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20criticized%20the%20high%20tariffs%20charged%20by%20India%20and%20other%20countries%20and%20termed%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20unfair%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20lawmakers%20from%20the%20US%20Capitol%2C%20Trump%20had%20announced%20that%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20will%20kick%20in%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20don't%20make%20your%20product%20in%20America%2C%20however%2C%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20you%20will%20pay%20a%20tariff%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20a%20rather%20large%20one.%20Other%20countries%20have%20used%20tariffs%20against%20us%20for%20decades%20and%20now%20it's%20our%20turn%20to%20start%20using%20them%20against%20those%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20average%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20China%2C%20Brazil%2C%20India%2C%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20%E2%80%94%20have%20you%20heard%20of%20them%3F%20And%20countless%20other%20nations%20charge%20us%20tremendously%20higher%20tariffs%20than%20we%20charge%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trump%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20very%20unfair.%20India%20charges%20us%20auto%20tariffs%20higher%20than%20100%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Trump%20has%20called%20India%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctariff%20king%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20abuser%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20joint%20press%20conference%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20White%20House%20last%20month%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20India%20has%20%E2%80%9Cbeen%20very%20strong%20on%20tariffs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20blame%20them%2C%20necessarily%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20different%20way%20of%20doing%20business.%C2%A0It's%20very%20hard%20to%20sell%20into%20India%20because%20they%20have%20trade%20barriers%2C%20very%20strong%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20had%20said%20that%20the%20US%20trade%20deficit%20with%20India%20is%20almost%20USD%20100%20billion%2C%20and%20he%20and%20Modi%20agreed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe'll%20begin%20negotiations%20to%20address%20the%20long-running%20disparities%20that%20should%20have%20been%20taken%20care%20of%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20didn't%20do%20that%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20US-India%20trading%20relationship%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20signing%20an%20agreement.%26quot%3B%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20is%20in%20Washington%20for%20trade%20talks%20with%20his%20US%20counterpart%20Howard%20Lutnick.%C2%A0%20As%20per%20US%20estimates%2C%20the%20US'%20total%20goods%20trade%20with%20India%20was%20an%20estimated%20USD%20129.2%20billion%20in%202024.%20US%20goods%20exports%20to%20India%20in%202024%20were%20USD%2041.8%20billion%2C%20up%203.4%20per%20cent%20(USD%201.4%20billion)%20from%202023.%20US%20goods%20imports%20from%20India%20totalled%20USD%2087.4%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20up%204.5%20per%20cent%20(USD%203.7%20billion)%20from%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20goods%20trade%20deficit%20with%20India%20was%20USD%2045.7%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20a%205.4%20per%20cent%20increase%20(USD%202.4%20billion)%20over%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741327260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ftuf95a4_donald-trump-narendra-modi_625x300_22_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-reiterates-very-high-tariff-nation-remark-for-india-7866837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20a%20very%20high%20tariff%20nation%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20said%20as%20he%20reiterated%20that%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20that%20impose%20levies%20on%20American%20goods%20will%20kick%20in%20on%20April%202.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-reiterates-very-high-tariff-nation-remark-for-india-7866837%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pastor%20Bajinder%20Singh%20booked%20for%20sexual%20harassment%20in%20Punjab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741327019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118777187%2Cimgsize-27160.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fviral-sensation-pastor-bajinder-singh-booked-for-sexual-harassment-in-punjab%2Farticleshow%2F118777246.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20complaint%20against%20Pastor%20Bajinder%20Singh%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Jalandhar%20district.%20A%20woman%20alleged%20that%20Singh%20harassed%20her%20at%20their%20church%20since%202017.%20Singh%20has%20been%20booked%20under%20multiple%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bad%20Touch%2C%20Mental%20Torture%3A%20%26quot%3BYeshu%20Yeshu%20Prophet%26quot%3B%20Bajinder%20Singh%20Faces%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Pastor%20Bajinder%20Singh%20of%20Glory%20and%20Wisdom%20Church%20after%20a%20woman%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20mental%20torture%20and%20intimidation.%20The%20woman%20said%20the%20Jalandhar-based%20pastor%2C%20who%20addresses%20himself%20as%20%26quot%3BProphet%20Bajinder%26quot%3B%2C%20sent%20her%20inappropriate%20messages%2C%20and%20threatened%20her%20and%20her%20family%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20taking%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20told%20reporters%20that%20she%20joined%20the%20church%20led%20by%20Singh%20in%202017%20and%20left%20it%20in%202023.%20In%202022%2C%20Singh%20allegedly%20made%20her%20sit%20alone%20in%20a%20cabin%20in%20the%20church%20on%20Sundays%20and%20allegedly%20hugged%20and%20touched%20her%20inappropriately%2C%20the%20complainant%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20torture%20began.%20%26quot%3BThey%20used%20to%20send%20cars%20after%20me%20when%20I%20went%20to%20college%2C%20which%20would%20follow%20me%20all%20the%20way%20home.%20They%20asked%20me%20if%20they%20want%20my%20father%20to%20never%20return%20home%20and%20if%20I%20want%20my%20mother%20to%20not%20leave%20the%20church%20alive.%20I%20was%20depressed%20and%20couldn't%20share%20the%20ordeal%20with%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20in%20Mohali.%20The%20woman%20also%20said%20that%20the%20past%20owns%20a%20large%20number%20of%20SIM%20cards%20and%20changes%20them%20regularly%20to%20contact%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20also%20alleged%20the%20pastor%20was%20involved%20in%20activities%20like%20opium%20trade%20and%20%26quot%3Bselling%20girls%20at%20GB%20Road%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20infamous%20area%20in%20Delhi%20known%20to%20house%20brothers.%20%26quot%3BThey%20commit%20wrong%20act%20with%20women%20and%20whoever%20speaks%20up%20is%20killed%20or%20intimidated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%20She%20further%20claimed%20to%20have%20a%20video%20of%20the%20head%20of%20the%20church%20Pradhan%20Avtar%2C%20in%20which%20he%20allegedly%20asking%20her%20to%20not%20bring%20external%20influence%20and%20settle%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20church.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20woman's%20husband%20said%20all%20evidence%2C%20including%20the%20pastor's%20video%20messages%20to%20her%20and%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20Avtar's%20visit%20to%20their%20residence%2C%20has%20been%20given%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe%20has%20not%20run%20away%20anywhere%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20two%20children%20at%20home%2C%20I%20am%20the%20father%20of%20small%20children%2C%20I%20can%20never%20do%20such%20a%20wrong%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20will%20take%20action%20against%20those%20who%20have%20wronged%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20pastor%20showed%20him%20addressing%20his%20audiences%20at%20a%20gathering%20where%20he%20urged%20them%20to%20help%20him%20get%20the%20women%20who%20have%20accused%20him%20to%20justice.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20their%20names%20and%20numbers%2C%20and%20I%20will%20tell%20you%20to%20whose%20house%20we%20have%20to%20go%20to%20with%20flags%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJalandhar%20district's%20ACP%20Babandeep%20Singh%20confirmed%20the%20woman%20came%20along%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20brother%20and%20husband%20to%20record%20her%20statement.%20Police%20said%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20him%20under%20sections%20354%20A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20354%20D%20(stalking)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20called%20for%20the%20pastor's%20arrest%20and%20victim's%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20has%20a%20considerable%20social%20media%20following%2C%20with%20his%20content%20often%20appearing%20in%20YouTube%20Shorts%20and%20Instagram%20Reels.%20He%20has%20over%20the%20months%20been%20endorsed%20by%20several%20celebrities%2C%20including%20ac