0been%20playing%20tennis%20since%20I%20was%20four%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETownsend%20said%20she%20underwent%20a%20C-section%20during%20delivery%2C%20which%20affected%20her%20recovery%20and%20journey%20back%20to%20the%20tennis%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20I%20finally%20got%20to%20the%20place%20where%20I%20could%20be%20active%2C%20moving%20my%20body%2C%20the%20core%20strengthening%20was%20the%20most%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20I'm%20still%20in%20a%20place%20where%20I'm%20still%20working%20on%20that%2C%20and%20my%20core%20is%20still%20not%20a%20hundred%20percent%20because%20of%20the%20damage%20that%20was%20done%20with%20the%20C-section.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETownsend%20said%20the%20C-section%20process%20was%20%26quot%3Btraumatic%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20is%20just%20something%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20constantly%20have%20to%20work%20on%20basically%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20because%20it's%20something%20that%20was%20just%20so%20traumatic%20for%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Townsend%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20It's%20definitely%20not%20anything%20that's%20just%20a%20one-time%20thing%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20sit-ups%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20crunches%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20planks%2C%20all%20the%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETownsend%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20women%20who%20had%20children%20typically%20retired%20from%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20I%20feel%20like%20we're%20in%20a%20place%20and%20in%20a%20time%20where%20women%20are%20having%20the%20ability%20to%20come%20back%20and%20play%20into%20their%20later%20years.%20I've%20even%20been%20playing%20my%20best%20tennis%20later%20in%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETatjana%20Maria%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tatjana%2