again%2C%26quot%3B%20Maria%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20start%20coming%20back%20after%20a%20child%2C%20you%20never%20know%20how%20it%20will%20go.%20I%20have%20to%20say%2C%20I%20have%20been%20really%20lucky%20with%20my%20body.%20I%20am%20not%20really%20the%20person%20who%20is%20injured%20a%20lot%2C%20so%20I%20hope%20it%20stays%20like%20this.%20I%20can%20play%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20I%20like%20to%20play%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomens-tennis-players-getting-parental-benefits-paid-maternal-leave-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741310605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ca2a79585f1dff88b16f22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomens-tennis-players-getting-parental-benefits-paid-maternal-leave-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Women's%20Tennis%20Association%20announced%20Maternity%20Fund%20Program%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20fund%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20Public%20Investment%20Fund.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomens-tennis-players-getting-parental-benefits-paid-maternal-leave-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20got%20clingy%20with%20my%20teen%20and%20feared%20she%20would%20push%20me%20away.%20I%20had%20to%20accept%20part%20of%20parenting%20meant%20letting%20her%20go.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222781%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20and%20teen%20taking%20a%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c744a769253ccddf983bc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20realized%20that%20now%20that%20her%20daughter%20is%20a%20teen%2C%20she's%20not%20the%20one%20who%20knows%20her%20the%20best.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EParenting%20my%20teen%20wasn't%20hard%20until%20I%20realized%20I%20wasn't%20ready%20to%20let%20her%20go.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20got%20weirdly%20clingy%20and%20was%20afraid%20I'd%20push%20her%20away.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERefocusing%20on%20myself%20helped%20me%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20future%20and%20a%20new%20version%20of%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20my%20daughter%20was%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fco-bathing-toddler-parenting-style-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eadorably%20cheeky%20toddler%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20seemed%20every%20older%20person%20I%20encountered%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BWait%20'til%20she's%20a%20teen!%26quot%3B%20before%20sharing%20some%20teenager-related%20horror%20story.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20hated%20all%20the%20negativity%20and%20refused%20to%20believe%20that%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-teens-is-a-balance-too-close-or-too-far-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edifficult%20parent-teen%20connection%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20inevitable.%20I%20worked%20hard%20to%20maintain%20a%20healthy%20relationship%2C%20and%20at%2017%2C%20my%20daughter%20rarely%20rolls%20her%20eyes%20at%20me.%20She%20still%20likes%20to%20hang%20out%2C%20has%20a%20kind%20boyfriend%20and%20an%20amazing%20group%20of%20friends%2C%20and%20is%20rocking%20high%20school.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wasn't%20prepared%20for%20the%20realization%20that%20hit%20me%20as%20I%20waved%20goodnight%20to%20her%20boyfriend%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%3B%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-advice-teenagers-dating-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno%20longer%20know%20her%20best%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Instead%20of%20sharing%20her%20secrets%20with%20me%2C%20she%20shares%20them%20with%20him%20or%20her%20besties%20in%20the%20group%20chat.%20While%20she's%20living%20her%20best%20life%2C%20I%20am%20coming%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20amazing%20human%20is%20spreading%20her%20wings%2C%20and%20my%20job%20is%20to%20stand%20back%2C%20watch%20her%20soar%2C%20and%20be%20a%20steady%2C%20soft%20place%20if%20she%20needs%20to%20crash%20land.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c48d00a-d300-4f95-9c4f-17cb6dd557f0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20my%20reaction%20to%20her%20growing%20independence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20a%20graduate%20degree%20in%20psychology%2C%20I%20understood%20this%20was%20a%20normal%2C%20healthy%20part%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpep-web.org%2Fbrowse%2Fdocument%2FPSC.022.0162A%3Fpage%3DP0162%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20adolescent%20individuation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20process%20that%20allows%20teens%20to%20fully%20develop%20their%20sense%20of%20self%20and%20become%20functioning%20adults.%20But%20nothing%20prepared%20me%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmolly-shannons-advice-parents-raising-teens-see-them-regular-people-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emessiness%20of%20my%20own%20emotions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20was%20horrified%20to%20find%20myself%20peppering%20her%20with%20questions%2C%20barging%20in%20on%20her%20conversations%2C%20and%20feeling%20hurt%20when%20her%20dad%20knew%20something%20I%20didn't.%20My%20sadness%20had%20me%20holding%20on%20tighter%20when%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20letting%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20feeling%20of%20grief%20is%20sometimes%20surprising%20to%20people%20because%20they%20don't%20see%20it%20as%20grief%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20my%20neighbor%20Carla%20Corral%2C%20a%20licensed%20clinical%20psychologist%20whose%20oldest%20daughter%20is%20a%20sophomore%20in%20college.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20losing%20somebody%2C%20right%2C%20to%20death%20or%20illness%20or%20the%20abrupt%20end%20of%20a%20relationship%2C%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-and-counselor-on-what-parents-should-know-about-grief-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit's%20grief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20didn't%20like%20the%20way%20my%20grief%20had%20me%20inserting%20myself%20into%20my%20daughter's%20life.%20I%20felt%20needy%2C%20clingy%2C%20and%20decidedly%20not%20cool.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20push%20her%20away%20or%20make%20her%20feel%20she%20needed%20to%20care%20for%20my%20feelings.%20It%20was%20time%20to%20get%20hold%20of%20myself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22911b9894-7c69-4285-a8a6-aecc94d99beb%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20to%20change%20my%20behavior%20or%20risk%20pushing%20her%20away%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20thought%20back%20to%20how%20exciting%20life%20was%20when%20I%20was%20her%20age%20and%20how%20eager%20and%20capable%20I%20felt.%20Shifting%20away%20from%20my%20current%20point%20of%20view%20as%20a%20concerned%20mom%20helped%20me%20see%20how%20smart%2C%20responsible%2C%20and%20prepared%20my%20daughter%20is.%20I%20also%20turned%20my%20attention%20back%20on%20myself%20and%20my%20dreams%20for%20the%20future.%20I%20grew%20up%20dancing%2C%20so%20I%20joined%20a%20tap%20class.%20It's%20great%20exercise%20and%20so%20much%20fun.%20Instead%20of%20gifts%20for%20Christmas%2C%20I%20gave%20my%20friends%20a%20breakfast%20or%20lunch%20date%20to%20prioritize%20connecting%20one-on-one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20journaling%20again%20to%20dump%20my%20worries%20on%20the%20page%20instead%20of%20on%20my%20daughter.%20This%20helped%20me%20see%20some%20of%20my%20concerns%20as%20ridiculous%20and%20others%20as%20important%20points%20to%20discuss%20before%20she%20leaves.%20I%20keep%20reminding%20myself%20my%20job%20as%20a%20parent%20is%20shifting%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20over.%20Making%20my%20life%20more%20about%20me%20again%20allowed%20those%20clingy%20behaviors%20to%20fade%20away%2C%20and%20when%20they%20occasionally%20pop%20up%2C%20I%20take%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20focus%20on%20something%20I%20enjoy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20soak%20up%20the%20time%20I%20have%20with%20her%20%E2%80%94%20including%20family%20movie%20nights%2C%20a%20spring%20break%20trip%20to%20visit%20her%20top%20choice%20university%2C%20and%20long%20conversations%20while%20walking%20the%20dog%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20building%20a%20list%20of%20things%20I%20want%20to%20do%20after%20she%20starts%20college%2C%20like%20visiting%20friends%2C%20volunteering%20for%20a%20local%20land%20trust%20and%20joining%20my%20husband%20for%20some%20of%20his%20work%20travel.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remind%20myself%20I've%20loved%20every%20stage%20of%20being%20a%20mom%2C%20even%20with%20the%20challenges%2C%20and%20I%20trust%20I%20will%20enjoy%20parenting%20a%20young%20adult.%20The%20part%20of%20my%20job%20that%20involved%20driving%20her%20around%20and%20making%20sure%20her%20homework%20was%20turned%20in%20may%20be%20done%2C%20but%20I%20know%20there%20are%20wonderful%20times%20ahead%20for%20both%20of%20us%2C%20together%20and%20apart.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-hardest-part-about-parenting-my-teen-is-letting-go-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741310462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c7465769253ccddf983c12%3F